 Resonance structure that could not be resolved but is present    8234 1451
 in transmission data sets were included to elastic and inelastic 8234 1451
 partial channels such that the total calculated cross section    8234 1451
 matches the experimental. Angular distributions for all          8234 1451
 reactions were calculated from CoH-3.                            8234 1451
